        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Welcome to my Scenes From the Month series!  In these posts, I share the highlights from my previous month ranging from the simple, everyday things to the more memorable events. One of the primary reasons that I blog is to keep a scrapbook that I can look back on in the future, and these posts help serve that purpose. Now that I have babies, everyday moments are extra special!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "March opened up with my grandmother's funeral. We got together as a family to celebrate her life, and it was really special. She will be missed dearly."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We ended the month with our first \"family of four\" vacation! We drove to Port Aransas for a long beach weekend. While it wasn't the super sunny weather we'd imagined for a beach trip, we had a great time. My in-laws joined, so Daniel and I got a date night out too!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Favorites from the Month:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "{This section contains some Amazon affiliate links.}"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Fiction Book"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://amzn.to/3sL6UeB",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Majesty"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " by Katharine McGee. This is the second book in the American Royals series. I really enjoyed it! I like the characters, and the plot line is so interesting. The series is about the modern-day American royal family. Such an interesting fictional world to follow."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Nonfiction Book"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://amzn.to/31FqT2H",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Unfinished"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " by Priyanka Chopra Jonas. I really, really enjoyed this book. What an interesting woman! I knew nothing about her before reading this book, but I love hearing about her life, her entry into the US acting world, her incredible work ethic, and her story of meeting Nick Jonas, falling in love, and getting married."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Music"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - Still on a Pandora kick. My latest favorite station is the \"Happy\" station. Such a fun mix of happy tunes!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Movie/TV"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - I've really enjoyed the new episodes of \"This is Us\" this month, especially the scenes on the early days of parenting. I can relate so much, and the character development and dialogue in that show is just beautiful."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Item"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - Our Peloton. Does that count as an item? I'm finally getting in some workouts during the week, and it actually seems to be helping with my dizzy symptoms. It's hard to have an excuse when I can literally get a 30 minute spin workout in without leaving my house. I'm also enjoying the yoga and stretching classes on the Peloton app."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Activity"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - Our beach trip was pretty special. It was the first time both boys went to the beach, and they had a blast. It was not a relaxing trip, but watching them play in the sand and the waves with such joy made it all worth it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Accomplishment"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " - Shopping for and planting our new plant babies in the backyard. This probably doesn't sound like a big accomplishment to most people, but we have never planted our own plants before. I feel super proud, and I hope they survive and thrive!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
