          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) Our amenity center did a fun event with Spiderman and an ice cream truck. Carson thoroughly enjoyed Spiderman and the ice cream. We didn't stay for the drive-in movie, but that will be a fun thing to do whenever the kiddos are a little older!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) Working with Daddy!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) Gramma and Grampa came for a visit. We always love when they are here. :)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) Caden LOVES this swing at the playground!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/SFTM_March-2021_EverydayAccountsBlog.com_2.png",
