                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) We welcomed a new member of our family during our beach trip. Bob the Turtle was found at the dolphin tour gift shop, and he has been glued to Carson ever since. We had a great time on the dolphin tour too! We saw so many dolphins!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) More beach time with Abuelo and Abuela! On this day, it was really overcast but not too cold to enjoy the day."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) Happy beach boy! His favorite activity was playing in the ocean waves."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) We stopped at the big shark at a gift shop in Port Aransas. Back when he was younger, Daniel took a picture in the shark on a trip with his church, so he wanted to get one with his family. My have times changed!"
          }
        ]
